== contrib/2gis ==

Additions provided by Artem Silenkov, 2gis [http://2gis.ru]

Written on bash & perl (so, not included in main part).

Included:

* memcached monitoring
* PostgreSQL streaming replication monitoring (postgres >= 9.0)
* PostgreSQL slow queries monitoring
* RabbidMQ monitoring
* Redis monitporing
* IPMI example template
* Sphinx status monitoring template

Installation:

* Copy zabbix-agent.d configs from /opt/ztc/contrib/2gis/conf/zabbix-agent.d/ to /etc/zabbix-agent.d/
* Copy scripts from /opt/ztc/contrib/2gis/bin/ to /opt/ztc/bin/
* Restart zabbix-agentd
* Import templates from /opt/ztc/contrib/2gis/templates/ using zabbix-web
